1.0.0.name: connect20/BotDefender_by_Lokad
1.0.0.description:
Protect your store from the automated retrieval of your prices by competitors.
Stop being outpriced every time you make a move. Best suited for retailers.

suggest.magento-hackathon\/magento-composer-inst: Allows to manage this package as a dependency
